  stimulus_text = 'The following text is from an article about the early development of the internet. The text explores how the internet changed the way people communicate and access information.  It discusses the development of the internet from its early stages to its current widespread use.  It explains how the internet has transformed the world in several ways.  It emphasizes the importance of the internet as a tool for connecting people and sharing knowledge.  The text also discusses some of the challenges that the internet has faced, such as censorship and privacy concerns.',
